    Class and Description
    Attribute
    The Attribute class represents an attribute in a relation
    FuncDep
    The FuncDep represents a functional dependency (FD), in which all the attributes on the left functionally determined all those on the right.
    FuncDep.Builder
    A builder class to help construct a FuncDep object
    Relation
    The Relation class represent a relation consisting a set of attributes and a set of FD's
